<i>Legend of Fei</i>

16
00:01:53,220 --> 00:01:56,140
<i>Episode 46</i>

17
00:01:58,640 --> 00:01:59,960
Li Sheng, Zhou Fei,

18
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,920
Lord Gantang is back safe and sound.

19
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:06,790
Cousin.

20
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:12,430
She’s... All yours.

21
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:26,360
I heard you need medicine

22
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:28,070
to suppress the poison in your system.

23
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,310
Killing you would be too easy.

24
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,440
So many people died of your poison.

25
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:34,870
It’s time for you

26
00:02:34,870 --> 00:02:36,720
to taste it yourself.

27
00:02:48,590 --> 00:02:50,110
When Shen Tianshu left,

28
00:02:50,110 --> 00:02:51,720
we should’ve known

29
00:02:52,440 --> 00:02:53,520
that he had decided

30
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:55,280
to sacrifice others if necessary.

31
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:56,800
You never would’ve guessed

32
00:02:56,800 --> 00:03:00,280
that’d be you, right?

33
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:08,280
He wouldn’t.

34
00:03:09,390 --> 00:03:11,590
Tianshu would never abandon me.

35
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,640
He’d come to get me out.

36
00:03:15,390 --> 00:03:17,670
He’d be here soon.

37
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:55,160
Grandfather, Aunt,

38
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:57,000
she’s finally paid

39
00:03:57,440 --> 00:03:59,160
for what she had done to you.

40
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:07,030
“I go to Wuzhou to see you

41
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:09,670
where mountains appear at dusk.

42
00:04:09,670 --> 00:04:11,670
Climb the mountain to
overlook the north of the river.

43
00:04:11,670 --> 00:04:13,920
Send stones and Ganoderma.

44
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:16,160
The valley is splendid

45
00:04:16,160 --> 00:04:19,000
where birds sing beautifully.

46
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:21,920
Music comes everywhere

47
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:25,670
when four songs are played”.

48
00:04:33,310 --> 00:04:36,520
Lord, is this poem

49
00:04:36,520 --> 00:04:38,720
the key to finding
The Color of Ocean and Heaven?

50
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:42,680
Liu Youliang guarded it with his life.

51
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,990
It must be useful.

52
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:49,750
The tokens are irregular

53
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:51,470
and suspicious.

54
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:53,800
Were they not,

55
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:56,640
The Color of Ocean and Heaven
would’ve been long gone.

56
00:04:56,640 --> 00:04:59,550
What should we do next?

57
00:05:00,150 --> 00:05:02,310
Tiankuang can go with you.

58
00:05:02,310 --> 00:05:03,520
-Lord.
-Lord Shen is occupied.

59
00:05:03,520 --> 00:05:04,750
-Move!
-Do not disturb.

60
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:11,800
Lu Tiankuang.

61
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,870
-Go away!
-You...

62
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:18,520
How did my sister die?

63
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:21,360
Are you blaming Lord Shen for her death?

64
00:05:21,870 --> 00:05:23,030
It was her fault

65
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:25,640
that she was weaker than others.

66
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:27,080
Gu Tianxian.

67
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:42,150
Are you accusing me of murder?

68
00:05:42,150 --> 00:05:44,150
Hadn’t you sent her to
the Fortress of the Forty-Eight,

69
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:45,960
she wouldn’t have died.

70
00:05:45,960 --> 00:05:48,550
When did I send her there?

71
00:05:49,470 --> 00:05:50,840
All she cared about

72
00:05:50,840 --> 00:05:52,470
was you.

73
00:05:52,470 --> 00:05:54,080
She only listened to you.

74
00:05:55,060 --> 00:05:55,620
<i>To Tianshu</i>

75
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:01,470
After she lost the Seal of Cautiousness,

76
00:06:01,470 --> 00:06:03,680
<i>Dear Tianshu</i>
I asked her to come back in the letter.

77
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:05,870
That was her response,

78
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:07,680
saying she had promised
Commander-in-chief

79
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:10,680
to retrieve the five tokens.

80
00:06:12,080 --> 00:06:13,920
You recognize her handwriting.

81
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,430
Read it yourself.

82
00:06:15,460 --> 00:06:18,340
<i>I won’t come back
until I have all five tokens.</i>

83
00:06:22,470 --> 00:06:24,430
Stop wasting your time on me.

84
00:06:24,430 --> 00:06:27,430
Save your strength to avenge her death.

85
00:06:29,360 --> 00:06:31,120
How did she die?

86
00:06:31,550 --> 00:06:34,200
The Snow-breaking Blade killed her.

87
00:06:34,680 --> 00:06:35,870
Zhou Fei!

88
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,430
Lord,

89
00:07:00,840 --> 00:07:01,520
I’m going to

90
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:03,430
fulfill her lifetime wish

91
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,310
to obtain Book of Almighty Medicine.

92
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,520
Please help me

93
00:07:09,840 --> 00:07:11,150
get revenge for her.

94
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:20,150
In that case,

95
00:07:20,150 --> 00:07:22,120
you must obey my orders.

96
00:07:33,470 --> 00:07:35,800
All the sacrifice is worth it

97
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:40,470
for The Color of Ocean and Heaven.

98
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:42,640
What do you think?

99
00:07:52,200 --> 00:07:55,800
You’re indeed skilled, Mr. Deng.

100
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:58,680
I’m not half as good as my master.

101
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:02,680
That’s too modest of you.

102
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:05,200
Few are as capable as you.

103
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:07,310
I’m not.

104
00:08:07,750 --> 00:08:10,310
I once read a book at my master’s,

105
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,120
titled Refinement of Iron,

106
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:14,200
in which skills of refining and smelting

107
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:15,240
are top-notch.

108
00:08:15,240 --> 00:08:17,120
They can make weapons

109
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,030
100 times better than those in use now.

110
00:08:19,030 --> 00:08:21,710
I’m nothing compared with my master.

111
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:26,480
You don’t believe me?

112
00:08:33,670 --> 00:08:35,000
Have a look.

113
00:08:36,920 --> 00:08:38,550
My master made this blade

114
00:08:38,550 --> 00:08:41,110
according to that book.

115
00:08:41,110 --> 00:08:42,600
Hold it.

116
00:08:49,040 --> 00:08:50,510
Cut this one.

117
00:08:50,510 --> 00:08:51,760
Go ahead.

118
00:08:58,640 --> 00:09:00,470
See? It’s true.

119
00:09:05,760 --> 00:09:07,790
Incredible!

120
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:11,880
I wish

121
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:15,350
I could have a glance at that book.

122
00:09:15,880 --> 00:09:18,320
I know. Me too.

123
00:09:19,030 --> 00:09:21,150
But it’s gone with my master.

124
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:22,790
I don’t think we can read it again.

125
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,350
You certainly can

126
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:28,080
