147
00:11:12,910 --> 00:11:14,470
I should’ve come back earlier.

148
00:11:19,350 --> 00:11:21,710
She’s poisoned with Worry-burying.

149
00:11:21,710 --> 00:11:22,910
According to Pathetic Clam,

150
00:11:22,910 --> 00:11:24,840
