158
00:11:47,910 --> 00:11:49,200
Really?

159
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:51,960
Yes.

160
00:12:31,660 --> 00:12:35,340
<i>True self</i>

161
00:13:33,590 --> 00:13:35,030
Fei,

162
00:13:35,760 --> 00:13:37,400
what you’re holding

163
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:39,440
isn’t Unbreakable, is it?

164
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,030
Father,

165
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:45,710
that one is broken.

166
00:13:48,280 --> 00:13:50,400
This is...

167
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,150
A gift from Xie Yun, right?

168
00:13:58,550 --> 00:14:00,670
It must’ve taken him

169
00:14:00,670 --> 00:14:02,760
a lot of effort

170
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:06,110
to find such a fine blade.

171
00:14:06,110 --> 00:14:08,000
He owed me one

172
00:14:08,000 --> 00:14:09,320
and he was obligated to pay me back.

173
00:14:19,550 --> 00:14:21,200
Fei,

174
00:14:21,200 --> 00:14:22,840
the so-called heaven’s will

175
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:27,200
or fate

176
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:31,230
is merely an excuse made by the weak.

177
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,910
We can’t run away from everything.

178
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,960
I know you

179
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,350
too well.

180
00:14:40,640 --> 00:14:42,670
You aren’t a quitter.

181
00:14:44,470 --> 00:14:47,080
You’ll fight to the end

182
00:14:47,590 --> 00:14:49,400
with your blade

183
00:14:49,640 --> 00:14:52,030
against the enemy.

184
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:58,760
