your responsibility?

218
00:19:08,230 --> 00:19:09,920
I thought

219
00:19:10,470 --> 00:19:13,590
we can put an end to everything

220
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:16,560
when we had all five tokens.

221
00:19:18,070 --> 00:19:20,070
