227
00:19:41,350 --> 00:19:42,920
I’m sorry.

228
00:19:44,110 --> 00:19:46,950
Don’t be.

229
00:19:46,950 --> 00:19:49,520
She didn’t keep them

230
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:51,710
for you,

231
00:19:51,710 --> 00:19:53,680
but for the greater good.

232
00:19:55,950 --> 00:19:57,800
So

233
00:19:57,800 --> 00:20:00,280
I’m the one

234
00:20:00,280 --> 00:20:02,680
who should apologize.

235
00:20:03,760 --> 00:20:08,190
I’m leaving for Penglai with Jinrong

236
00:20:08,190 --> 00:20:11,710
to have Abbot Tongming treat her.

237
00:20:15,920 --> 00:20:19,190
All that started with me.

238
00:20:19,190 --> 00:20:20,470
I knew

239
00:20:20,470 --> 00:20:23,310
