to have them destroyed.

240
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:27,190
So

241
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:28,710
from now on,

242
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:31,230
I’ll try to locate the treasure

243
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:34,000
to draw an end

244
00:20:34,000 --> 00:20:35,310
to everything.

245
00:20:38,430 --> 00:20:42,430
