246
00:20:45,230 --> 00:20:47,400
Think about it.

247
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:51,520
If it fell into the Demons’ hands,

248
00:20:51,520 --> 00:20:53,640
a catastrophe would rise.

249
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:56,520
