You know,

286
00:25:22,500 --> 00:25:24,730
Aunt is always strong.

287
00:25:24,730 --> 00:25:26,930
She’ll be fine, right?

288
00:25:26,930 --> 00:25:28,610
Don’t worry too much.

289
00:25:29,420 --> 00:25:32,090
She wouldn’t leave us behind.

290
00:25:34,660 --> 00:25:36,180
Chuchu,

291
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:38,060
I’ve been thinking

292
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:40,260
if I had practiced hard

293
00:25:40,260 --> 00:25:41,970
instead of slacking,

294
00:25:41,970 --> 00:25:44,500
I would’ve been as skilled as Fei

295
00:25:44,500 --> 00:25:46,730
and I could’ve protected others.

296
00:25:46,730 --> 00:25:48,090
That way, Aunt wouldn’t have...

297
00:25:48,810 --> 00:25:50,660
I know you’re upset

298
00:25:50,660 --> 00:25:53,140
and eager to improve your skills,

299
00:25:53,730 --> 00:25:56,180
but what happened isn’t your fault.

300
00:25:56,180 --> 00:25:57,970
Don’t beat yourself up.

301
00:25:57,970 --> 00:25:59,330
I used to believe

302
00:25:59,330 --> 00:26:01,930
there were no good or bad people,

303
00:26:01,930 --> 00:26:03,450
only their stands

304
00:26:03,450 --> 00:26:05,690
and views were different.

305
00:26:05,690 --> 00:26:07,380
But I was wrong.

306
00:26:07,380 --> 00:26:10,500
Some are born evil.

307
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:12,570
They mean to destroy

308
00:26:12,570 --> 00:26:15,610
what others cherish
by fair means or foul.

309
00:26:15,610 --> 00:26:17,900
I admit that I’m less skilled

310
00:26:17,900 --> 00:26:19,420
and talented than others,

311
00:26:19,420 --> 00:26:21,180
but other than martial arts,

312
00:26:21,180 --> 00:26:23,690
there are other weapons I can use

313
00:26:24,300 --> 00:26:25,780
just like those in this book.

314
00:26:26,380 --> 00:26:28,610
I want to be like Ying Hecong

315
00:26:28,610 --> 00:26:30,810
and kill those Demons myself!

316
00:26:31,970 --> 00:26:33,850
Gentlemen know what to do

317
00:26:33,850 --> 00:26:35,140
and what not to do.

318
00:26:35,140 --> 00:26:36,730
Is it wrong

319
00:26:36,730 --> 00:26:39,610
to kill bad people?

320
00:26:40,690 --> 00:26:41,930
Take poison

321
00:26:41,930 --> 00:26:43,930
as an example.

322
00:26:43,930 --> 00:26:45,610
Both Ying Hecong

323
00:26:45,610 --> 00:26:47,500
and Pathetic Clam use it.

324
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:48,780
Do you know

325
00:26:48,780 --> 00:26:50,850
the difference between them?

326
00:26:51,730 --> 00:26:53,260
I do, Chuchu.

327
00:26:54,300 --> 00:26:55,570
The last thing we want

328
00:26:55,570 --> 00:26:58,380
is to see you drown yourself in hatred.

329
00:26:58,380 --> 00:27:00,380
I’m more worried about Fei.

330
00:27:00,380 --> 00:27:02,300
Ever since Pathetic Clam died,

331
00:27:02,300 --> 00:27:04,810
she’s locked herself in the room.

332
00:27:04,810 --> 00:27:06,180
Mr. Xie is there with her.

333
00:27:06,180 --> 00:27:08,610
He’ll comfort her.

334
00:27:08,610 --> 00:27:11,060
I know how she feels,

335
00:27:11,610 --> 00:27:12,930
but

336
00:27:12,930 --> 00:27:16,380
that woman’s death
couldn’t repair the damage.

337
00:27:16,380 --> 00:27:19,540
Xie Yun and Aunt

338
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:21,970
are dying because of her,

339
00:27:21,970 --> 00:27:23,020
but

340
00:27:23,020 --> 00:27:25,780
the mastermind got away with it.

341
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,210
Nobody can handle

342
00:27:28,210 --> 00:27:29,660
such pain.

343
00:27:30,380 --> 00:27:32,180
Fei can.

344
00:27:34,300 --> 00:27:35,260
Everyone,

345
00:27:35,500 --> 00:27:37,780
remember how Old Master took you in?

346
00:27:37,780 --> 00:27:40,540
I could never repay him
for his kindness.

347
00:27:40,540 --> 00:27:43,300
We all know how bad the situation is.

348
00:27:43,300 --> 00:27:44,330
No one can help us.

349
00:27:44,330 --> 00:27:45,330
That’s right.

350
00:27:45,330 --> 00:27:48,140
What if the Demons raided us again

351
00:27:48,140 --> 00:27:49,060
just like the last time?

352
00:27:49,060 --> 00:27:50,380
Look,

353
00:27:50,380 --> 00:27:51,900
we must stay together

354
00:27:51,900 --> 00:27:53,970
in times like this.

355
00:27:53,970 --> 00:27:55,660
We can’t fall apart

356
00:27:55,660 --> 00:27:57,540
from inside.

357
00:27:59,260 --> 00:28:01,380
Fei is here. You can tell her

358
00:28:01,380 --> 00:28:03,020
what you think.

359
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:06,660
We never force people to do anything.

360
00:28:06,660 --> 00:28:08,420
You’re free to stay or leave.

361
00:28:08,420 --> 00:28:09,300
Fei,

362
00:28:09,300 --> 00:28:11,210
don’t get me wrong,

363
00:28:11,210 --> 00:28:13,090
but other than Madam Li,

364
00:28:13,090 --> 00:28:15,060
who can take charge of the Fortress?

365
00:28:15,060 --> 00:28:16,260
We’re old

366
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:18,450
and almost got killed
by the Demons more than once.

367
00:28:18,450 --> 00:28:20,260
It’s probably too much

368
00:28:20,260 --> 00:28:21,930
to ask for a peaceful retirement.

369
00:28:21,930 --> 00:28:23,210
Leader Niu,

370
00:28:23,210 --> 00:28:26,540
we’re grateful for your service

371
00:28:26,540 --> 00:28:28,180
all these years.

372
00:28:28,180 --> 00:28:30,930
If you ever wish to come back,

373
00:28:30,930 --> 00:28:32,420
our Fortress

374
00:28:32,420 --> 00:28:34,570
is always open to you.

375
00:28:35,730 --> 00:28:36,690
Elders,

376
00:28:36,690 --> 00:28:38,930
I’m here to tell you

377
00:28:38,930 --> 00:28:40,060
that I’m leaving

378
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:42,810
to look for
The Color of Ocean and Heaven.

379
00:28:42,810 --> 00:28:44,090
And I’m entrusting you

380
00:28:44,450 --> 00:28:46,380
with things here.

381
00:28:46,380 --> 00:28:47,610
You can’t, Fei.

382
00:28:47,610 --> 00:28:49,540
I know how much you hate them.

383
00:28:49,540 --> 00:28:51,140
But don’t act on impulse.

384
00:28:51,140 --> 00:28:52,060
What if something happens...?

385
00:28:52,060 --> 00:28:55,210
Trust me. I know what I’m doing.

386
00:28:55,810 --> 00:28:57,330
As long as the Demons

387
00:28:57,330 --> 00:28:59,180
are after The Color of Ocean and Heaven,

388
00:28:59,180 --> 00:29:00,610
we’ll always

389
00:29:00,610 --> 00:29:02,500
be in danger,

390
00:29:02,500 --> 00:29:03,850
and so will

391
00:29:03,850 --> 00:29:05,930
the rest of all sects.

392
00:29:05,930 --> 00:29:07,970
We can’t run away from them.

393
00:29:12,210 --> 00:29:14,260
“I go to Wuzhou to see you

394
00:29:14,260 --> 00:29:16,540
where mountains appear at dusk.

395
00:29:16,540 --> 00:29:18,780
Climb the mountain to
overlook the north of the river.

396
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:21,500
Send stones and Catalpa branches”.

397
00:29:22,730 --> 00:29:23,660
Lord Gu,

398
00:29:23,660 --> 00:29:26,060
where’s the entrance of
the Big Medicine Valley?

399
00:29:26,060 --> 00:29:28,210
It’s right in this poem.

400
00:29:30,500 --> 00:29:32,610
“Where mountains appear at dusk”.

401
00:29:33,690 --> 00:29:36,420
We’re surrounded by mountains.

402
00:29:38,780 --> 00:29:41,210
“Climb the mountain to
overlook the north of the river”.

403
00:29:42,570 --> 00:29:45,020
“The north of the river”?

404
00:29:45,660 --> 00:29:47,930
What’s there to look?

405
00:29:48,900 --> 00:29:51,090
Open your eyes

406
00:29:51,420 --> 00:29:53,020
and check carefully.

407
00:29:53,380 --> 00:29:56,660
Let me know

408
00:29:56,660 --> 00:29:57,930
if there’s anything matching the poem.

409
00:29:57,930 --> 00:29:58,660
Yes.

410
00:29:59,060 --> 00:30:00,420
Lord Gu!

411
00:30:01,610 --> 00:30:02,660
Lord Gu!

412
00:30:02,660 --> 00:30:04,500
There’s a strange place

413
00:30:04,500 --> 00:30:05,900
where irregular rocks pile on.

414
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:31,810
“Where mountains appear at dusk”.

415
00:30:33,450 --> 00:30:35,900
Is this it?

416
00:30:38,930 --> 00:30:41,210
Check the surroundings
for anything unusual.

417
00:30:41,210 --> 00:30:42,180
Yes.

418
00:30:52,300 --> 00:30:53,450
Anything?

419
00:30:53,450 --> 00:30:54,540
What did you see?

420
00:30:54,540 --> 00:30:55,540
Lord Gu,

421
00:30:55,540 --> 00:30:57,610
there’s nothing strange.

422
00:31:00,660 --> 00:31:03,180
“Send stones and Catalpa branches”.

423
00:31:07,930 --> 00:31:09,540
Did you see Catalpa trees

424
00:31:09,540 --> 00:31:11,060
on our way here?

425
00:31:11,060 --> 00:31:12,330
Trees are many,

426
00:31:12,330 --> 00:31:14,210
but not of that species.

427
00:31:15,090 --> 00:31:17,180
That can’t be!

428
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:20,210
The entrance

429
00:31:20,210 --> 00:31:22,260
must be nearby.

430
00:31:25,090 --> 00:31:27,330
Hurry up.

431
00:31:27,330 --> 00:31:27,970
Yes.

432
00:31:27,970 --> 00:31:29,500
Be careful.

433
00:31:29,730 --> 00:31:30,780
Don’t drop anything.

434
00:31:30,780 --> 00:31:31,660
Got it.

435
00:31:34,180 --> 00:31:36,020
-Be careful. Slowly.
-Leader Niu.

436
00:31:36,020 --> 00:31:38,380
These are all from Miss Zhou.

437
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:39,730
What are they?

438
00:31:39,730 --> 00:31:41,660
Knowing that we’re heading to the north,

439
00:31:41,660 --> 00:31:43,900
she’s prepared
thick clothes and food for us.

440
00:31:43,900 --> 00:31:44,610
And

441
00:31:44,610 --> 00:31:46,140
herbs, too.

442
00:31:47,090 --> 00:31:48,810
She said you practice a lot

443
00:31:48,810 --> 00:31:50,420
and suffer from leg pain.

444
00:31:50,420 --> 00:31:51,540
Apply the herbs to your injury

445
00:31:51,540 --> 00:31:53,140
and you’ll feel better.

446
00:31:53,930 --> 00:31:55,930
She’s considerate.

447
00:31:55,930 --> 00:31:57,140
Where is she?

448
00:31:57,140 --> 00:31:58,380
On the training field.

449
00:31:59,060 --> 00:32:00,380
You may leave.

450
00:32:01,450 --> 00:32:02,090
Put it over there.

451
00:32:02,090 --> 00:32:03,330
Got it.

452
00:32:04,930 --> 00:32:06,780
Li Zheng’s granddaughter

453
00:32:07,730 --> 00:32:10,060
wouldn’t dare to lie to me.

454
00:32:11,380 --> 00:32:12,690
Then...

455
00:32:13,060 --> 00:32:13,850
Then I must’ve

456
00:32:13,850 --> 00:32:16,300
missed something in the poem.

457
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:18,970
But I swear

458
00:32:19,730 --> 00:32:21,610
I’ve done my best.

459
00:32:22,610 --> 00:32:23,970
Never mind.

460
00:32:26,810 --> 00:32:28,930
What should we

461
00:32:28,930 --> 00:32:31,380
do next?

462
00:32:43,300 --> 00:32:45,260
A jade ox.

463
00:32:45,690 --> 00:32:48,810
When I came across it months ago,

464
00:32:48,810 --> 00:32:51,060
I thought it’d be to your taste,

465
00:32:51,060 --> 00:32:53,380
so I kept it for you.

466
00:32:57,260 --> 00:32:58,380
That’s

467
00:32:58,380 --> 00:33:00,180
too kind of you.

468
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,260
As you know,

469
00:33:03,260 --> 00:33:04,570
my brother and I...

470
00:33:06,380 --> 00:33:09,330
I work under him

471
00:33:09,330 --> 00:33:11,210
and dare not to offend him.

472
00:33:11,210 --> 00:33:12,610
Hold on.

473
00:33:12,610 --> 00:33:15,570
Just hear me out.

474
00:33:15,570 --> 00:33:17,730
What I’m saying is

475
00:33:17,730 --> 00:33:21,180
he’s above you now,

476
00:33:21,180 --> 00:33:23,780
but might not be forever,

477
00:33:23,780 --> 00:33:25,500
right?

478
00:33:28,260 --> 00:33:30,540
We’re friends.

479
00:33:30,540 --> 00:33:33,970
If one day, I take his place,

480
00:33:34,610 --> 00:33:36,060
this kind of accessory

481
00:33:36,060 --> 00:33:39,330
might be too cheap for you.

482
00:33:44,930 --> 00:33:46,730
This jade piece is spotless

483
00:33:46,730 --> 00:33:48,570
as if it were a masterpiece of nature.

484
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:51,730
It’s a rare treasure.

485
00:33:52,660 --> 00:33:55,140
No one deserves it other than you.

486
00:33:55,140 --> 00:33:56,970
I’m glad you like it.

487
00:33:56,970 --> 00:33:58,540
Report!

488
00:34:01,330 --> 00:34:02,210
Commander,

489
00:34:02,210 --> 00:34:03,850
you have a visitor.

490
00:34:03,850 --> 00:34:05,330
Who is it?

491
00:34:05,330 --> 00:34:06,900
A man surnamed Shen.

492
00:34:09,020 --> 00:34:10,380
It’s time

493
00:34:10,380 --> 00:34:12,500
for me to leave.

494
00:34:14,810 --> 00:34:17,090
Thanks for your gift.

495
00:34:17,090 --> 00:34:19,540
If you need anything from me,

496
00:34:19,540 --> 00:34:21,780
just let me know.

497
00:34:44,730 --> 00:34:47,100
Have a seat, Lord Shen.

498
00:34:58,020 --> 00:35:00,370
To what do I owe

499
00:35:00,370 --> 00:35:02,300
the honor?

500
00:35:05,020 --> 00:35:07,060
The Color of Ocean and Heaven.

501
00:35:09,580 --> 00:35:11,860
I heard the tokens

502
00:35:11,860 --> 00:35:14,620
are all in Zhou Fei’s hand.

503
00:35:15,820 --> 00:35:18,580
I can’t do anything about it.

504
00:35:19,650 --> 00:35:22,210
Not anymore.

505
00:35:22,210 --> 00:35:24,580
They belong to me now.

506
00:35:27,020 --> 00:35:29,890
Congratulations!

507
00:35:30,930 --> 00:35:33,730
There’s a confusing poem

508
00:35:33,730 --> 00:35:36,370
about the treasure,

509
00:35:36,370 --> 00:35:38,500
and I couldn’t figure it out.

510
00:35:38,500 --> 00:35:41,860
I understand you own tons of talents...

511
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:43,620
Lord Shen,

512
00:35:47,130 --> 00:35:50,130
they’re useless

513
00:35:52,170 --> 00:35:55,860
compared with your people.

514
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:58,620
Besides, you’ve warned me to stay away

515
00:35:58,620 --> 00:36:01,650
from what’s inside the treasure.

516
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:05,300
Why should I help you?

517
00:36:09,370 --> 00:36:11,970
I’ve seldom asked others for favors

518
00:36:12,410 --> 00:36:14,580
and I won’t take back

519
00:36:14,580 --> 00:36:16,500
what I’ve said.

520
00:36:16,500 --> 00:36:17,650
You may be a deterrent

521
00:36:17,650 --> 00:36:20,860
to other sects,

522
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:22,650
but compared with

523
00:36:22,650 --> 00:36:25,690
my formidable troops,

524
00:36:25,690 --> 00:36:27,690
you’re nothing.

525
00:36:29,130 --> 00:36:30,650
So what

526
00:36:35,100 --> 00:36:37,860
if I turn you down?

527
00:36:45,300 --> 00:36:46,690
Your troops

528
00:36:46,690 --> 00:36:48,780
may be formidable,

529
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:52,620
but they can’t stop me

530
00:36:52,620 --> 00:36:55,410
from taking a person’s life.

531
00:36:55,410 --> 00:36:57,060
Trust me,

532
00:36:57,060 --> 00:37:00,650
or go back to your tent

533
00:37:00,650 --> 00:37:02,930
and wait for it.

534
00:37:14,370 --> 00:37:15,650
I’m not

535
00:37:15,650 --> 00:37:18,650
an ingrate.

536
00:37:18,650 --> 00:37:21,500
Once I obtain that treasure,

537
00:37:22,930 --> 00:37:24,820
I’ll do my utmost

538
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:28,450
to help you fulfill your wish.

539
00:37:58,540 --> 00:38:00,060
Tiankuang,

540
00:38:00,450 --> 00:38:02,860
I can find the entrance

541
00:38:03,620 --> 00:38:05,860
on my own.

542
00:38:07,060 --> 00:38:09,450
That treasure concerns our future.

543
00:38:09,450 --> 00:38:11,690
We can’t be too careful.

544
00:38:19,170 --> 00:38:20,500
Lords,

545
00:38:20,500 --> 00:38:22,130
the poem shows

546
00:38:22,130 --> 00:38:23,260
the entrance

547
00:38:23,260 --> 00:38:25,370
is most likely to be here.

548
00:38:26,060 --> 00:38:29,170
But some of the lines are wrong.

549
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:31,970
Really?

550
00:38:37,890 --> 00:38:40,890
No wonder I didn’t find it.

551
00:38:40,890 --> 00:38:41,730
The good news is

552
00:38:41,730 --> 00:38:43,210
we can use the surroundings

553
00:38:43,210 --> 00:38:44,300
to locate it.

554
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,370
How long will it take?

555
00:38:45,370 --> 00:38:46,650
About two hours.

556
00:38:46,650 --> 00:38:47,820
Make it quick.

557
00:38:56,500 --> 00:38:57,690
Sheng,

558
00:38:58,730 --> 00:39:00,370
have some food.

559
00:39:02,820 --> 00:39:04,650
What’s on your mind?

560
00:39:06,500 --> 00:39:09,300
Fei says she’s going to get
The Color of Ocean and Heaven

561
00:39:09,780 --> 00:39:11,500
but the Demons have all the tokens.

562
00:39:11,500 --> 00:39:12,930
As skilled as she is,

563
00:39:12,930 --> 00:39:14,170
she’s still

564
00:39:14,170 --> 00:39:15,580
not Shen Tianshu’s match.

565
00:39:18,210 --> 00:39:19,340
Sheng,

566
00:39:19,340 --> 00:39:20,650
are you saying

567
00:39:20,650 --> 00:39:22,340
Fei is looking for
The Color of Ocean and Heaven?

568
00:39:24,210 --> 00:39:26,260
I know where it is.

569
00:39:26,820 --> 00:39:28,690
It’s in the Big Medicine Valley.

570
00:39:29,370 --> 00:39:32,020
Who told you that?

571
00:39:32,020 --> 00:39:34,970
Pathetic Clam and Shen Tianshu said it.

572
00:39:34,970 --> 00:39:36,650
It’s true.

573
00:39:38,930 --> 00:39:41,130
Li Sheng, I was just told

574
00:39:41,130 --> 00:39:42,650
Demons Manor had dispatched a squad

575
00:39:42,650 --> 00:39:43,820
to the north.

576
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:45,970
Their destination is unknown yet.

577
00:39:51,340 --> 00:39:51,930
Go tell

578
00:39:51,930 --> 00:39:54,130
Zhou Fei and Xie Yun
to meet me at the Hall of Elders

579
00:39:54,130 --> 00:39:55,580
for an emergency.

580
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:56,580
Yes.

581
00:39:57,370 --> 00:39:58,540
Yan,

582
00:39:58,540 --> 00:39:59,970
ask Yang Jin to come over, too.

583
00:39:59,970 --> 00:40:01,020
Got it.

584
00:40:02,410 --> 00:40:03,210
Let’s go.

585
00:40:06,130 --> 00:40:08,690
It’s in the Big Medicine Valley?

586
00:40:08,690 --> 00:40:09,820
That’s right.

587
00:40:09,820 --> 00:40:11,970
Shen Tianshu and Pathetic Clam said so.

588
00:40:12,780 --> 00:40:15,210
Lyu Run’s disciple founded
the Big Medicine Valley.

589
00:40:15,210 --> 00:40:17,410
And he himself wrote
Book of Almighty Medicine.

590
00:40:18,170 --> 00:40:19,820
That book

591
00:40:19,820 --> 00:40:21,540
is highly likely to be there.

592
00:40:23,260 --> 00:40:24,410
General Huang, Huang Shenbian,

593
00:40:24,410 --> 00:40:26,410
was the son of Lyu Run’s disciple.

594
00:40:26,410 --> 00:40:27,780
It makes sense

595
00:40:27,780 --> 00:40:29,580
that he’d keep the treasure

596
00:40:29,580 --> 00:40:31,500
at that secluded valley.

597
00:40:31,500 --> 00:40:32,370
Besides,

598
00:40:32,370 --> 00:40:33,580
Pathetic Clam and Shen Tianshu

599
00:40:33,580 --> 00:40:34,970
had all the tokens then.

600
00:40:34,970 --> 00:40:36,890
Why would they lie to a girl?

601
00:40:36,890 --> 00:40:38,540
It’s said the entrance

602
00:40:38,540 --> 00:40:41,020
is trapped and concealed.

603
00:40:41,020 --> 00:40:43,370
The poem Liu Youliang left behind

604
00:40:43,370 --> 00:40:46,820
must be the clue.

605
00:40:46,820 --> 00:40:48,860
Anything new about the Demons?

606
00:40:48,860 --> 00:40:50,100
All we know is

607
00:40:50,100 --> 00:40:52,210
they’re heading to the north,

608
00:40:52,210 --> 00:40:54,730
probably in the direction of
the Big Medicine Valley.

609
00:40:54,730 --> 00:40:56,500
If so, let’s go.

610
00:40:56,500 --> 00:40:57,210
Yes.

611
00:40:57,210 --> 00:40:58,540
Hold your horses.

612
00:40:59,650 --> 00:41:01,450
That poem is still a mystery.

613
00:41:01,450 --> 00:41:03,170
If we leave unprepared...

614
00:41:03,170 --> 00:41:04,500
Stop dragging your feet.

615
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:07,370
Instead of pondering over

616
00:41:07,370 --> 00:41:09,500
those words such as
“mountains” and “dusk”,

617
00:41:10,500 --> 00:41:12,210
why don’t we go there and have a look?

618
00:41:12,210 --> 00:41:13,970
I agree.

619
00:41:14,730 --> 00:41:16,130
But...

620
00:41:16,130 --> 00:41:17,130
Sheng,

621
00:41:17,130 --> 00:41:18,650
Fei is right.

622
00:41:18,650 --> 00:41:20,060
It’s better than

623
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:22,020
sitting here and doing nothing.

624
00:41:29,260 --> 00:41:31,410
If you’ve made up your mind,

625
00:41:31,410 --> 00:41:33,100
I’ll go with you.

626
00:41:33,930 --> 00:41:35,260
I can

627
00:41:35,260 --> 00:41:37,620
deal with traps there.

628
00:41:37,620 --> 00:41:38,210
I meant

629
00:41:38,210 --> 00:41:40,340
to have you stay

630
00:41:40,340 --> 00:41:41,890
and take care of things here.

631
00:41:42,540 --> 00:41:45,260
It’s imperative to find that treasure.

632
00:41:45,260 --> 00:41:46,820
We need all hands on deck

633
00:41:46,820 --> 00:41:47,930
and end things once and for all.

634
00:41:47,930 --> 00:41:48,820
Besides,

635
00:41:48,820 --> 00:41:52,260
the risk is high this time.

636
00:41:52,260 --> 00:41:54,340
The more the help, the better.

637
00:41:55,130 --> 00:41:56,820
Li Sheng is right.

638
00:41:56,820 --> 00:41:58,410
We can’t let you two go there alone.

639
00:41:58,410 --> 00:42:00,860
We aren’t too skilled,

640
00:42:00,860 --> 00:42:03,210
but we can still be of help.

641
00:42:03,210 --> 00:42:04,210
Yang Jin,

642
00:42:04,970 --> 00:42:06,020
this is

643
00:42:06,020 --> 00:42:06,820
our family matter

644
00:42:06,820 --> 00:42:08,860
and I hate to drag you into it.

645
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:10,450
It’s just...

646
00:42:10,450 --> 00:42:11,730
If...

647
00:42:11,730 --> 00:42:13,340
things go wrong,

648
00:42:13,340 --> 00:42:14,580
I hope

649
00:42:14,580 --> 00:42:16,620
you can take care of my sister.

650
00:42:16,620 --> 00:42:19,860
I’m officially

651
00:42:19,860 --> 00:42:21,930
entrusting her to you.

652
00:42:25,450 --> 00:42:26,580
You...

653
00:42:28,690 --> 00:42:30,410
What are you doing?

654
00:42:30,410 --> 00:42:32,540
I can take care of myself.

655
00:42:32,540 --> 00:42:33,970
And

656
00:42:33,970 --> 00:42:35,650
I don’t need him.

657
00:42:36,450 --> 00:42:38,540
Now isn’t the time for this.

658
00:42:38,540 --> 00:42:40,780
I’m not afraid of death.

659
00:42:41,890 --> 00:42:42,860
Yang Jin,

660
00:42:42,860 --> 00:42:44,780
what about your valley?

661
00:42:46,730 --> 00:42:47,820
The Small Medicine Valley

662
00:42:47,820 --> 00:42:50,020
is built to triumph over evil.

663
00:42:50,020 --> 00:42:51,340
If I could get hold of

664
00:42:51,340 --> 00:42:53,650
rare medical books,

665
00:42:54,210 --> 00:42:56,820
those elders would be thrilled.

666
00:42:57,410 --> 00:42:59,260
They’d trade me for them if necessary.

667
00:43:01,730 --> 00:43:04,970
Is there such a rule in their sect?

668
00:43:07,540 --> 00:43:08,410
Yang Jin,

669
00:43:08,410 --> 00:43:10,450
I know I can’t stop you,

670
00:43:10,450 --> 00:43:11,620
but think about it.

671
00:43:11,620 --> 00:43:14,300
Only two girls are left here.

672
00:43:14,300 --> 00:43:15,890
What if...

673
00:43:15,890 --> 00:43:18,370
Sheng, you don’t know anything.

674
00:43:18,370 --> 00:43:19,860
Chuchu and I have decided

675
00:43:19,860 --> 00:43:21,170
to join you.

676
00:43:23,730 --> 00:43:25,620
I thought you knew better than her.

677
00:43:25,620 --> 00:43:27,450
How come you’re on her side?

678
00:43:27,450 --> 00:43:28,930
Yan,

679
00:43:28,930 --> 00:43:31,020
you’d better stay at home.

680
00:43:31,020 --> 00:43:32,370
We’ll get things done.

681
00:43:32,370 --> 00:43:33,780
What are you talking about?

682
00:43:33,780 --> 00:43:34,930
That poem

683
00:43:34,930 --> 00:43:36,300
started with me.

684
00:43:36,300 --> 00:43:37,580
I must go with you.

685
00:43:38,340 --> 00:43:39,300
Li Yan!

686
00:43:39,300 --> 00:43:40,690
Sheng,

687
00:43:40,690 --> 00:43:42,370
I’m no longer a kid.

688
00:43:42,370 --> 00:43:43,450
I can do

689
00:43:43,450 --> 00:43:44,410
as much as you do.

690
00:43:44,410 --> 00:43:45,780
This isn’t a game.

691
00:43:45,780 --> 00:43:46,690
It’s different.

692
00:43:46,690 --> 00:43:48,500
That’s why I’m coming with you.

693
00:43:48,500 --> 00:43:49,970
Aunt treated me so well.

694
00:43:49,970 --> 00:43:51,540
I must do something for her.

695
00:43:51,540 --> 00:43:53,100
Enough. I’ve made up my mind.

696
00:43:53,690 --> 00:43:54,620
Sheng,

697
00:43:55,340 --> 00:43:56,970
I know you want to protect her,

698
00:43:56,970 --> 00:43:59,370
but can you do that forever?

699
00:43:59,370 --> 00:44:00,340
So

700
00:44:00,340 --> 00:44:02,340
you should respect her decision.

701
00:44:03,690 --> 00:44:05,540
Are you sure about this?

702
00:44:07,020 --> 00:44:09,100
Since my parents were killed,

703
00:44:09,260 --> 00:44:11,100
I’ve decided

704
00:44:11,820 --> 00:44:14,500
to not run away from anything.

705
00:44:14,500 --> 00:44:16,210
I’ll fight side by side with you

706
00:44:16,210 --> 00:44:18,500
to the end.

707
00:44:25,540 --> 00:44:26,580
Zhou Fei,

708
00:44:26,580 --> 00:44:28,130
say something!

709
00:44:29,650 --> 00:44:31,170
I was weak

710
00:44:31,170 --> 00:44:32,930
when I first left home

711
00:44:32,930 --> 00:44:35,620
and I was near death more than once.

712
00:44:35,620 --> 00:44:37,620
Masters I met along the way

713
00:44:38,100 --> 00:44:40,210
never told me to give up.

714
00:44:40,210 --> 00:44:42,300
They all trusted me instead.

715
00:44:43,340 --> 00:44:44,410
Cousin,

716
00:44:44,410 --> 00:44:46,130
none of us wants to quit.

717
00:44:46,130 --> 00:44:47,820
Stop wasting your time.

718
00:44:47,820 --> 00:44:49,130
Let’s go.

719
00:44:51,540 --> 00:44:53,020
Alright. It’s settled.

720
00:44:53,020 --> 00:44:53,890
Whatever comes our way,

721
00:44:53,890 --> 00:44:55,580
we’ll handle it together.

722
00:44:59,860 --> 00:45:00,730
Please!

723
00:45:01,130 --> 00:45:02,210
Fine.

724
00:45:02,970 --> 00:45:04,370
Enemies are still out there.

725
00:45:04,370 --> 00:45:06,020
Damage can’t be undone.

726
00:45:06,540 --> 00:45:09,300
Let’s end everything with us.

727
00:45:09,300 --> 00:45:10,930
-Yes!
-Let’s go!

728
00:45:13,280 --> 00:45:15,600
<i>Hall of Elders</i>

729
00:45:15,600 --> 00:45:19,320
<i>Fortress of the Forty-Eight</i>

730
00:45:25,300 --> 00:45:26,370
Fei,

731
00:45:27,930 --> 00:45:29,340
We’re ready

732
00:45:29,340 --> 00:45:31,300
to go anytime.

733
00:45:33,210 --> 00:45:34,970
Fei,

734
00:45:34,970 --> 00:45:37,970
this trip is full of danger

735
00:45:37,970 --> 00:45:39,370
and the unknown.

736
00:45:39,690 --> 00:45:40,780
Listen,

737
00:45:41,020 --> 00:45:42,860
