738
00:45:42,860 --> 00:45:43,890
I’m always here with you.

739
00:45:43,890 --> 00:45:45,690
You aren’t alone.

740
00:45:46,730 --> 00:45:49,020
I’ll kill

741
00:45:49,020 --> 00:45:51,100
whoever gets in my way.

742
00:45:53,930 --> 00:45:55,930
Look at you.

743
00:45:55,930 --> 00:45:57,450
When you’re quiet,

744
00:45:57,450 --> 00:45:58,930
you’re pretty

745
00:45:58,930 --> 00:46:00,970
and lovely.

746
00:46:00,970 --> 00:46:02,410
Once you speak,

747
00:46:02,410 --> 00:46:05,410
others will be in awe of you.

748
00:46:05,970 --> 00:46:08,260
You sure can be trusted.

749
00:46:08,890 --> 00:46:10,450
They say

750
00:46:10,970 --> 00:46:13,500
the Demons are a never-ending nightmare.

751
00:46:14,340 --> 00:46:17,340
But I believe however long it lasts,

752
00:46:17,340 --> 00:46:19,860
the ray of light will tear it apart.

753
